{"toc":[],"part_attrs":{"title":"Skins and Bones \/ 皮肉和骨头","cjk_count":0,"sub_title":"伊朗 \/ 旅行 \/ LOMO笔记","is_original":1,"orig_title":"","en_count":0,"gallery_mode":1,"gallery_theme":"night","group_id":68408,"id":140897,"people":{"translator":[],"orig_author":[],"author":[63690688]}},"pages":[{"data":{"layout":"C","seq":27934599,"title":"cover_top.jpg","dimension":"S","legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[]},"type":"container"},"size":{"large":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-large\/public\/27934599.jpg","width":544,"height":367},"smallshow":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-smallshow\/public\/27934599.jpg","width":1035,"height":700},"tiny":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-tiny\/public\/27934599.jpg","width":181,"height":122},"orig":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-largeshow_web\/public\/27934599.jpg","width":1035,"height":700}}},"expandable":true,"type":"illus","id":43574631},{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"22张LOMO照片，一些在旅途中收集的零碎小物，简短、朴实的文字，就组成了这样一本小册子，记录了我在伊朗独自旅行的22天。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"这些琐碎的东西，不过是展现了我对伊朗的匆匆一瞥，没有什么对这个国家的深入了解或剖析，而是通过这种简单的、随意的、甚至是自言自语式的记录，勾画出在这样一段独自旅行中，那些平凡的经历所带来的细微的内心体验。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container","id":43574632},{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"在德黑兰的最后几天里，一位出租车司机给我写下几句鲁米的诗，大致意思是：“我是百分之百的自我，余下的，是我的皮肉和骨头。”","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"回国后，我整理出这些我在伊朗用玩具相机拍的照片，以及那些我在旅途中收集的小物，这些东西将我又带回到那一个个旅途中的场景――然后，我又想起了这首诗――于是我将这些照片和小物赋予“皮肉和骨头”的概念，而这些“皮肉和骨头”所带有的温度，总是不经意地、轻轻地触动着“我自己”。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"  ","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container","id":43574633},{"data":{"layout":"C","seq":27934318,"title":"skins and bones1B.jpg","dimension":"S","legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"“我是百分之百的自我，余下的，是我的皮肉和骨头。”","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"  ","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"size":{"large":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-large\/public\/27934318.jpg","width":544,"height":367},"smallshow":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-smallshow\/public\/27934318.jpg","width":1035,"height":700},"tiny":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-tiny\/public\/27934318.jpg","width":181,"height":122},"orig":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-largeshow_web\/public\/27934318.jpg","width":1035,"height":700}}},"expandable":true,"type":"illus","id":43574634},{"data":{"layout":"C","seq":27934818,"title":"skins and bones2A.jpg","dimension":"S","legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"伊朗民兵组织Basij风格的围巾，这个符号让人联想起在两伊战争中为国捐躯的战士，就像在伊朗的许多城市，你都能看到那些纪念这些烈士的宣传画。有的时候，这些符号就像一个个伤疤，时刻提醒着人们这个国家所遭受过的痛苦。另一方面，现在很多年轻人又对这些符号表现出不屑和厌恶：它们象征着严厉的伊斯兰教法和政府管制。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"  ","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"size":{"large":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-large\/public\/27934818.jpg","width":544,"height":367},"smallshow":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-smallshow\/public\/27934818.jpg","width":1035,"height":700},"tiny":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-tiny\/public\/27934818.jpg","width":181,"height":122},"orig":{"src":"http:\/\/img3.douban.com\/view\/ark_works_pic\/gallery-largeshow_web\/public\/27934818.jpg","width":1035,"height":700}}},"expandable":true,"type":"illus","id":43574635}]}